  "detailed_description": "Rescue breakfast in this arcade-style bullet hell shoot 'em up!<br><br>A strange curse falls across the land! Breakfast everywhere has disappeared, and it's up to you to save the most important meal of the day! Blast your way through 5 colorful stages jam-packed with dangerous enemies, elaborate bullet patterns, and ruthless bosses to rescue breakfast once and for all!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2474690/extras/8d38f350fcfaca7ad8cad9493589fef5.poster.avif?t=1701320512\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2474690/extras/8d38f350fcfaca7ad8cad9493589fef5.webm?t=1701320512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2474690/extras/8d38f350fcfaca7ad8cad9493589fef5.mp4?t=1701320512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Release the shoot button to charge a powerful piercing shot! Hit multiple enemies for extra points and stars!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2474690/extras/ab890476efe5e97d4a42e3e2d9508f06.poster.avif?t=1701320512\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2474690/extras/ab890476efe5e97d4a42e3e2d9508f06.webm?t=1701320512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2474690/extras/ab890476efe5e97d4a42e3e2d9508f06.mp4?t=1701320512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect stars to fill your Superbeam meter! Unleash your Superbeam in dense bullet patterns for huge bonuses!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2474690/extras/24918f2849b010df78b661b23aa70b93.poster.avif?t=1701320512\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2474690/extras/24918f2849b010df78b661b23aa70b93.webm?t=1701320512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2474690/extras/24918f2849b010df78b661b23aa70b93.mp4?t=1701320512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Save Nat's buddy, Sam, for extra firepower!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>5 Exciting Stages!<br></li><li>Over 50 Unique Enemies!<br></li><li>3 Powerful Magic Types!<br></li><li>2 Challenging Difficulty Modes!<br></li><li>about 30 minutes of gameplay</li></ul><br><i>Cover art by the talented MisMash!</i>",
  "about_the_game": "Rescue breakfast in this arcade-style bullet hell shoot 'em up!<br><br>A strange curse falls across the land! Breakfast everywhere has disappeared, and it's up to you to save the most important meal of the day! Blast your way through 5 colorful stages jam-packed with dangerous enemies, elaborate bullet patterns, and ruthless bosses to rescue breakfast once and for all!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2474690/extras/8d38f350fcfaca7ad8cad9493589fef5.poster.avif?t=1701320512\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2474690/extras/8d38f350fcfaca7ad8cad9493589fef5.webm?t=1701320512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2474690/extras/8d38f350fcfaca7ad8cad9493589fef5.mp4?t=1701320512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Release the shoot button to charge a powerful piercing shot! Hit multiple enemies for extra points and stars!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2474690/extras/ab890476efe5e97d4a42e3e2d9508f06.poster.avif?t=1701320512\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2474690/extras/ab890476efe5e97d4a42e3e2d9508f06.webm?t=1701320512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2474690/extras/ab890476efe5e97d4a42e3e2d9508f06.mp4?t=1701320512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect stars to fill your Superbeam meter! Unleash your Superbeam in dense bullet patterns for huge bonuses!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akama